1. Kada *osetim* tvoj miris, srce mi zaigra. (When I *sense* your scent, my heart skips a beat.)
2. Moram *da osetim* hranu pre nego što je jedem. (I need *to feel* the food before I eat it.)
3. Kada me neko uvredi, *osećam* se jako loše. (When someone offends me, I *feel* very bad.)
4. Da li *osećaš* se umorno nakon posla? (Do you *feel* tired after work?)
5. Kada udišem miris lavande, odmah *osećam* se opušteno. (When I inhale the scent of lavender, I immediately *feel* relaxed.)
6. Volim da *osećam* sunčeve zrake na koži. (I love to *feel* the sun rays on my skin.)
7. Nadam se da ću *osećati* sreću celog mog života. (I hope that I will *feel* happiness throughout my entire life.)
8. *Osetio sam* jaku bol u stomaku nakon što sam pojeo previše slatkiša. (I *felt* a strong pain in my stomach after eating too many sweets.)
9. Ona je *osećala* ljubav prema njemu još od prvog dana. (She *felt* love towards him since the first day.)
10. Uvek *osetim* olakšanje kada završim sve svoje obaveze. (I always *feel* relieved when I finish all of my tasks.)